{
  "text": "In addition, the utilization of an explicit memory (e.g. reference set), controlling the search diversity, and a dynamic manipulation of the population size are also recommended for a better performance of hybrid metaheuristics [CITATION_1] . A good performance is presented by maintaining a balance between diversification and intensification of the search. Therefore, the SS is chosen for this study, due to its capability in maintaining a balance between diversification and intensification of the search.",
  "citation_candidates": [
